{"blocks":[{"key":"ddaq3","text":"Wash sections thoroughly with a phosphate-buffered saline(PBS,  ,  ) solution.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":63,"length":1},{"key":1,"offset":66,"length":1}],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"concentration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"concentration":"0.01","error_concentration":false,"guid":"FB2E41F027B511ED92527D65A2540975","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"unit":21}},"1":{"type":"ph","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"guid":"FF58158027B511ED92527D65A2540975","id":0,"number":"7.4"}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"cn7a1","text":"Incubate the sections in a PBS solution containing the appropriate biotinylated secondary antibody (1:200; Vector Labs, Burlingame, CA, USA) combined with 1% normal serum, 0.3% Triton X-100, and 1% BSA for   at  .","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":206,"length":1},{"key":1,"offset":211,"length":1}],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":5400,"guid":"8041996027B511ED92527D65A2540975","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}},"1":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"8314B69027B511ED92527D65A2540975","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"","unit":32}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ckk3u","text":"Rinse the sections in PBS twice followed by a third rinse in TRIS buffer ( ;  ).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":74,"length":1},{"key":1,"offset":77,"length":1}],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"concentration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"concentration":"0.05","error_concentration":false,"guid":"D159CAC027B511ED92527D65A2540975","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"unit":21}},"1":{"type":"ph","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"guid":"D59096A027B511ED92527D65A2540975","id":0,"number":"7.6"}}}}
